{"tid":2110992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"昨倒掛塗污國旗 患末期直腸癌古思堯被控侮辱國旗 申保釋遭嚴舜儀拒絕","createTime":"2020-07-16T09:11:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T13:05:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8a16c42b9d5f3ed5ee0403e81aabd1f1b19f2e7b","tid":2110992,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:11:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075552&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n36crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=d29c73d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075552&h=8e0fd0c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075552</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）昨日15名民主派人士就4宗煽惑未經批准集結案到西九龍裁判法院應訊，開庭前社運人士古思堯在法院大樓外揮動一面上下倒轉，兼寫上「白色恐怖」等字的國旗，被警方當場拘捕。他今（16日）被控一項侮辱國旗罪，原訂於西九龍裁判法院提堂，惟因古在九龍城裁判法院有另一案需處理，故轉往該法院提堂。古拒絕由律師代表，庭上親自申請保釋，但遭裁判官拒絕，須還柙至8月27日再訊。"},{"pid":"9660f0ff1bbfc1cc210f32d0ef690e84d7256531","tid":2110992,"uid":259507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"[Reddit 線唔夠人呀] 首個 Reddit task 精選上線啦!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2110936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2110936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81a3b3a92d0744ee24a2a67c8019a75f367aae7e","tid":2110992,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79775fe90e3755321f70b3a947238bdcf724543d","tid":2110992,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9660f0ff1bbfc1c